subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Frank Lickliter II shot a par 72 yesterday in Winter Garden, Fla., to take a three-stroke lead after the fourth of six rounds in the PGA Tour National Qualifying Tournament. The top 25 finishers and ties will earn 2008 PGA Tour cards.
